  <name>OptiScaler Client</name>
  <summary>Install OptiScaler seamlessly</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      OptiScaler Client is a modern utility designed to simplify the installation, 
      management, and update of the OptiScaler mod. It provides a native experience 
      for gamers looking to enhance their titles with upscaling technologies.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Auto-Scanner for Steam, Epic, GOG, and more.</li>
      <li>One-Click installation for OptiScaler versions.</li>
      <li>Deep-Clean uninstall to safely remove files.</li>
      <li>Full localization support.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
